  <ml:body>
    <ml:teaser>
We are excited to announce the participants for the upcoming DemoJam on May 3rd, sponsored
by our partners, <a href="http://www.avalonconsult.com/">Avalon Consulting LLC</a>.
The DemoJam will start promptly at 5pm on the Pacific Terrace of the Intercontinental Hotel.
At 5PM, Matt Turner and Norm Walsh will draw the random order.
Participants will then be called to the stage in that order and given 300 seconds to impress the 
crowd and take home an iPad.
    </ml:teaser>
